	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <persName ref="person1647">Sebastiano</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="person1647">Sebastian Meyer</persName> (vgl. Anm. 1).</note> videbo.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam mihi ipsi sic videtur esse inutile ad concordiam, si diutius istic sit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qualis tu esse legatus <placeName ref="place121">Helvetiorum</placeName> velles in<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>vor</hi> in <hi>gestrichenes</hi> audivi.</note> hoc concordię negotio, audivi<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Bullinger hatte in seinem Brief an <persName ref="person28">Bucer</persName> vom 6. Oktober dessen Schreiben an <persName ref="person138">Luther</persName> vom 19. Januar kritisiert und kurz skizziert, wie er selbst argumentiert hätte; s. oben <ref target="file11096">Nr. 1053</ref>, 96-106.</note>.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed, ut pace tua dicam, parum attineat hoc ad rem.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Res est, uter recte causam sacramenti intelligat.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In ea qui fungi recte sequestris<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>vor</hi> sequestris <hi>ein gestrichenes, unlesbares Wort.</hi></note> officio vult, apud <persName ref="person138">Lutherum</persName> concedet non prorsus nos rem intellexisse aut, si intellexerimus, non ita expressisse, ut sentiebamus.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vide, sic apud <persName ref="person138">Lutherum</persName> est agendum necessario, et[?] qui se praebere volet medium in hac quidem causa, ut<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c"><hi>kann auch als</hi> at <hi>oder</hi> ac <hi>gelesen werden.</hi></note> aliter non potest<note xml:id="fnd" type="footnote" n="d"><hi>vielleicht als</hi> possit <hi>zu lesen.</hi></note>, apud nos sic dicet: <persName ref="person138">Lutherus</persName> aliter nunc sentit,<note xml:id="fne" type="footnote" n="e">sensit <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note> quam olim sensit aut certe quam scripsit olim.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">At neque hic ratio sequestrandi alia est.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed de his alias.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Te quaeso, ut in omni negotio Christi Christi<note xml:id="fnf" type="footnote" n="f"><hi>Die ersten drei Buchstaben</hi> des <hi>zweiten</hi> Christi <hi>in Majuskeln.</hi></note> sis, sic ut es, et te regno eius impertias totum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><pb type="edition" next="310"/>Hos viros<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Unbekannt.</note> valde cupio ut omni officio humanitatis excipias.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, mi frater dulcissime.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta mihi <persName ref="person14">Theodorum</persName><note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="person14">Theodor Bibliander</persName>.</note> et fratres diligenter.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person81">Gryneus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino Heinricho Bullingero, fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
